WEBVTT

00:06:28.300 --> 00:06:31.509
jer ukoliko ne trče brže, postaće ručak.

00:06:31.509 --> 00:06:34.395
Dakle, ovo je igra 
koju igramo sa bakterijama,

00:06:34.395 --> 00:06:36.452
izuzev što mi nismo gepardi,

00:06:36.452 --> 00:06:37.929
mi smo gazele,

00:06:37.929 --> 00:06:40.716
i bakterija bi,

00:06:40.716 --> 00:06:42.549
samo tokom ovog kratkog govora,

00:06:42.549 --> 00:06:43.975
dobila decu i unuke

00:06:43.975 --> 00:06:46.360
i shvatila kako da bude otporna

00:06:46.360 --> 00:06:48.834
samo selekcijom i 
proverom raznih mogućnosti,

00:06:48.834 --> 00:06:50.746
upornim pokušavanjem.

00:06:50.746 --> 00:06:54.518
A kako da preduhitrimo bakteriju?

00:06:54.518 --> 00:06:56.572
Imamo procese otkrivanja lekova,

00:06:56.572 --> 00:06:58.202
ispitivanje molekula,

00:06:58.202 --> 00:06:59.930
imamo klinička testiranja,

00:06:59.930 --> 00:07:02.078
a onda, kada mislimo da imamo lek,